------Change the Drive------
command: cd /d PathInFileManager


------Search for Folder------
command: dir "wantedFolderName" /s/p


------Open Task Manager------
ctrl+Shift+esc
it's for reach the extensin of file for open and close apps

------Open App------
command: start AppName.extensionName


------Close App------
taskkill /im AppName.extensionName ==> if i add /f it will close with unsaved changes


------Create Folder------
command: mkdir titleOfDirectory
example: mkdir Topics\Programming
         mkdir CV\my\c\v\1\2 ....
